short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Can't find the maps link? Use this extension to open your search in Google Maps.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Having trouble reaching a Maps location from a Google search? This extension makes it easy.

- Open your search in Google Maps easily.
- Fully transparent and accessible.
- No data collection.
- Open source.
